Wreck-It Ralph;;86;;87;;PG;;Arcade-game character Wreck-It Ralph (John C. Reilly) is tired of always being the "bad guy" and losing to his "good guy" opponent, Fix-It Felix (Jack McBrayer). Finally, after decades of seeing all the glory go to Felix, Ralph decides to take matters into his own hands. He sets off on a game-hopping trip to prove that he has what it takes to be a hero. However, while on his quest, Ralph accidentally unleashes a deadly enemy that threatens the entire arcade.;;Animation,Adventure,Kids & family,Comedy;;Rich Moore;;2012;;John C. Reilly,Sarah Silverman,Jack McBrayer,Jane Lynch,Alan Tudyk,Mindy Kaling,Joe Lo Truglio,Ed O'Neill,Dennis Haysbert,Adam Carolla,Horatio Sanz,Edie McClurg,Roger Craig Smith,Gerald C. Rivers,Rachael Harris,Stefanie Scott,Reuben Langdon,Kyle Hebert;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wreck_it_ralph